### Educational Material Addendum
This repository serves as an educational resource and an expanded practical guide. It is fundamentally inspired by and based upon the theoretical framework of the ["Prompt Engineering for ChatGPT"](https://www.coursera.org/learn/prompt-engineering) specialization offered by [Vanderbilt University](https://www.vanderbilt.edu/) via Coursera. 

The original prompt engineering concepts, academic theories, and course structures remain the intellectual property of their respective creators and institutions. The MIT License above applies to the original examples, structural formatting, markdown handbook compilation, GitHub Actions workflows, and automated scripts created by the repository maintainer.
